isecurity and collects extensive data, the random number generation		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ispeed is very slow. This can be observed using the rngtest tool from		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ithe rng-tools package:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
